title: Mandela Barnes jumps into Wisconsin governor race — but baggage from his 2022 Senate bid follows
description: Former Wisconsin Lt. Gov. Mandela Barnes launched his campaign for governor as the likely Democratic primary frontrunner despite baggage from his 2022 Senate race loss.
content:
